commit.message:
Fix build with Qt 5.15 (missing QPainterPath includes)

Thanks-to: Petr Zima <zima@matfyz.cz>
~ Fix missing header
Fix tab order for margin spin boxes
~ Fix: the cancel shortcut of color pickup interaction was active even when the interaction wasn't which caused conflicts with other shortcuts

Make some shortcuts work on different keyboard layouts

Use QShortcut instead of comparing Qt::Key in key event handlers. QApplication has the internal platform specific key map that allows QShortcut's to capture a pressed key independently of the current keyboard layout.
~ Inline some short methods to increase performance

~ Implement ConnectionManager to reduce repeating code and ease its maintenance

Relates to 2c5f817775dae8704da859b861c17d7283e4a8c3

~ Don't use unique_ptr for QObject* members with this parent

Their lifetime is managed by their parents as it is.
~ Use std::shared_ptr instead of intrusive_ptr
~ Add CMake DEVELOPER_VERSION option to enable the internal debug features
~ Fix a possible lag on switching filter on large projects
Change the key combination for dragging a guide to Ctrl+Alt+LMB
Allow dragging the page in lasso zone creation mode by pressing any modifier key (Shift, Ctrl, Alt) with LMB

Add shortcut to manually reload page (F5 key)

Useful at the output stage on modifying the source image
Reprocess output if the source image has been modified
Fix visual glitches around thumbnails at the margins stage

Improvements and fixes in deviation highlighting feature:

1. Threshold is coupled to mean value.
2. Fixed value calculation on the selection content stage.
3. Deviation of the hard margins values is highlighted on the margins stage.
~ Remove the unused font from ui files

Add buttons to scale thumbnails to the thumbnails panel and respective shortcuts

Shortcuts: `Crtl++` to magnify and `Ctrl+-` to diminish thumbnails
Add deviation highlighting button to the thumbnail panel
~ Disable drawBase property of QTabBar in the themes stylesheet
~ Don't use hard-coded enum values as keys for ColorParams to conform open-closed principle
Fix: horizontal original alignment was incorrectly parsed from XML
~ Remove all the info listeners when ImageView hidden

~ Refactor content mask feature

Build content mask in the working thread.
Move the functionality relating to content mask from ImageView classes.

~ Consistent naming of local variables

Relates to 4ae9c7438fa4820a7919a50d861e1663e5b7ff9b

Improvements and new features on zones interaction

* Zone creation mode:
  Press `Z` to switch to polygonal mode.
  Press `X` to switch to lasso (free drawing) mode.
  Press `C` to switch to rectangular mode.
  Press `Z` or `X` while creating a new zone to switch between polygonal and rectangular modes respectively.
* Zone vertex:
  `D` when the cursor is over a zone vertex - delete the vertex.

* Improved lasso mode behavior: start creating a new zone immediately on LMB press without the first point and automatically complete on closure.

* Zone creation mode icon is shown in the status bar.
~ Fix: CMAKE_POSITION_INDEPENDENT_CODE and CMAKE_INSTALL_RPATH_USE_LINK_PATH weren't in cache
Fix warnings on launching
